Case Based, Rule Learning

Case Based Reasoning (CBR) is mentioned in the paper as a technique used to resolve current design issues by considering previous similar situations. This falls under the sub-category of Case Based AI. 

Rule Learning is present in the system's support for defeasible and qualitative reasoning, which involves the use of rules to make decisions based on uncertain or incomplete information. This falls under the sub-category of Rule Learning AI.
